# ============================================================================
# AZ'ARCH ADDITIONS -- everything below is added by Az'arch (edit here)
# ============================================================================
# NOTE: calamares and librewolf ARE listed here (so pacstrap installs them), but
# their PACKAGE FILES come from Az'arch's OWN recipes built into the offline repo
# (libraries/azarch/config/pkgbuild.py), not from the Arch mirrors. Their
# Arch-repo runtime dependencies are also listed below. Every name below was
# verified present in the Arch core/extra repos (or, for calamares/librewolf, in
# the Az'arch local repo).

# --- Az'arch's own packages (built by the makepkg stage into the local repo) ---
calamares
librewolf

